ActivityManager ActivityCollector.java<pre><code>public class ActivityCollector {
public static List&lt;Activity&gt; acs = new LinkedList&lt;Activity&gt;();
public static void add(Activity ac){
acs.add(ac);
}
public static void remove(Activity ac){
acs.remove(ac);
}
public static void finishAll(){
for(Activity ac : acs){
ac.finish();
}
}
}
</code></pre> Activity的收集 <p>在所有重写的<code>onCreate()</code>和<code>onDestroy()</code>方法中，分别添加<code>ActivityCollector.add(this)</code>和<code>ActivityCollector.remove(this)</code></p> <p>在特定的时候执行<code>ActivityCollector.finishAll()</code>关闭所有Activity</p>

